The Daily: The Rise of Nationalism Across the Globe

In this week's podcast, we hosted a live conversation from "The Daily", The New York Times'
flagship podcast. In an event in partnership with The New York Times, we were joined by the
podcast's host Michael Barbaro, as well as Berlin Bureau Chief Katrin Bennhold, London-
based International Correspondent Ellen Barry, Executive Producer Theo Balcomb and
Producer Clare Toeniskoetter for a conversation about the implications of the nationalist

undercurrent currently sweeping across Europe.
